{"tid":2435691,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"五年前，屯門大興邨，皇宮大酒樓門口嗰檔泊車檔，開張大吉。","createTime":"2021-03-06T12:20:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T11:29:41.000Z","uid":93615,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7428ea1c0bd82669d4d48ab1f133bacdfc9f4ecb","tid":2435691,"uid":93615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:20:08.000Z","msg":"我同埋成班兄弟雄心壯志。點知開張唔夠半個月，平均每日俾人掃檔一點三次。一年內，死咗六個兄弟。 <br />\n<br />\n佛祖保祐。我呢條命叫做「一將功成萬骨枯」。不過我唔同意。我認為我哋出嚟行嘅。係生係死應該由自己決定。"},{"pid":"5f8c39cee074be2b0127ed8fb40572bc9437d6e8","tid":2435691,"uid":1781,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:23:01.000Z","msg":"泊車都死咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"486c3dab4eb39a30f3c8363d7db87741b8293290","tid":2435691,"uid":337336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"你呢條命剋死咁多兄弟，仲要萬骨枯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b834df792e6b20101a08868764344e6939961ffc","tid":2435691,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea0872e3f91cd75b8933a4cb7c707d858c003ab","tid":2435691,"uid":93615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b834df792e6b20101a08868764344e6939961ffc","tid":2435691,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"睇親都笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}